text: Komp Georg Ignaz Komp (5 June 1828, in Hammelburg – 11 May 1898, in Mainz) was a Roman Catholic clergyman who was Bishop of Fulda. He was appointed Archbishop of Freiburg but died en route to his enthronement. ==References== ==Sources== * Category:Bishops of Fulda Category:Archbishops of Freiburg Category:1828 births Category:1898 deaths Category:People from Bad Kissingen (district)
